.
├── app #----> Just a folder
│   ├── configModule.cfg --- > file Contaiing Concfiguration Details for the flask app
│   ├── __init__.py      ----> Direction for interpreter to treat this folder as a python Module
│   ├── models.py        ----> Contains database related functions
│   ├── 
│   └── search           ----> Blueprint/module which deals with the search functionality
│       ├── forms.py
│       ├── __init__.py  ----> Treat Search as a Module
│       ├── 
│       ├── static       ----> Contains static files realated to search blueprint
│       ├── templates    ----> Contains templates realated to search blueprint
│       │   ├── form.html
│       │   └── results.html
│       └── views.py     ----> Views and routing for the search blueprint
├── 
├── requirements.txt     ----> List of required packages for the app
├── runapp.py            ----> Python file to call the app.run() method
└── tests                ----> Folder Containing Tests
    ├── __init__.py
    ├── __pycache__
    │   ├── __init__.cpython-34.pyc
    │   └── tests.cpython-34.pyc
    └── tests.py

